Dialogue: 1,0:01:03.15,0:01:04.43,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,现在回到
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.15,0:01:04.43,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We now return
Dialogue: 1,0:01:04.43,0:01:07.68,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,今晚的恐怖电影剧场  播出的是
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.43,0:01:07.68,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,to tonight's Creepy-Time Theater presentation of
Dialogue: 1,0:01:07.68,0:01:09.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,机器人之夜
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.68,0:01:09.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,"Night of the Robot"
Dialogue: 1,0:01:13.88,0:01:16.63,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,小蜗快来  机器人恐怖电影开播了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.88,0:01:16.63,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hurry, Gary, the scary robot movie's on
Dialogue: 1,0:01:18.56,0:01:20.68,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你说我不该看是什么意思
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.56,0:01:20.68,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What do you mean I shouldn't watch this?
Dialogue: 1,0:01:20.68,0:01:23.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,恐怖电影从来吓不到我
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.68,0:01:23.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Scary movies don't always freak me out
Dialogue: 1,0:01:25.48,0:01:27.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,万一我妈是机器人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.48,0:01:27.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What if Mom is a robot?
Dialogue: 1,0:01:27.82,0:01:29.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,万一谢尔曼叔叔是机器人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.82,0:01:29.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What if Uncle Sherm is a robot?
Dialogue: 1,0:01:30.36,0:01:32.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,万一小蜗是机器人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.36,0:01:32.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What if Gary is a robot?
Dialogue: 1,0:01:33.22,0:01:34.24,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,小蜗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.22,0:01:34.24,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Gary?
Dialogue: 1,0:01:35.91,0:01:36.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,小蜗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.91,0:01:36.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Gary?
Dialogue: 1,0:01:37.66,0:01:38.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,小蜗蜗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.66,0:01:38.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Gare-bear?
Dialogue: 1,0:01:40.95,0:01:43.09,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,小蜗  你要是机器人的话
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.95,0:01:43.09,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Gary, if you were a robot
Dialogue: 1,0:01:43.09,0:01:44.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一定会跟我说吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.09,0:01:44.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,you'd tell me, right?
Dialogue: 1,0:01:47.19,0:01:48.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没什么好怕的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.19,0:01:48.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I got nothing to worry about
Dialogue: 1,0:01:49.08,0:01:51.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,来好好睡上一觉
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.08,0:01:51.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And now to get a good night's sleep
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.39,0:02:04.56,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(378,488)}蟹堡王
Dialogue: 1,0:02:07.56,0:02:08.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,机器人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.56,0:02:08.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Robot
Dialogue: 1,0:02:08.07,0:02:09.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我的老天爷
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.07,0:02:09.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, my gosh
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.81,0:02:11.23,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(722,662)}海土豆
Dialogue: 1,0:02:14.57,0:02:17.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,来边听音乐边数钱吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.57,0:02:17.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,How about a little music to count me money to?
Dialogue: 1,0:02:17.50,0:02:20.21,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,现在播放的是裤头村头号金曲
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.50,0:02:20.21,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And now for the number-one song in Bikini Bottom
Dialogue: 1,0:02:20.21,0:02:21.31,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,电子动物园
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.21,0:02:21.31,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,"Electric Zoo"
Dialogue: 1,0:02:25.26,0:02:26.44,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还挺上头
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.26,0:02:26.44,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's pretty catchy
Dialogue: 1,0:02:26.75,0:02:29.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,哔哔啵吧  哔哔啵哔
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.75,0:02:29.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Bee-bee-boo-bop, bee-bee-boo-beep
Dialogue: 1,0:02:30.01,0:02:31.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,真不错
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.01,0:02:31.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah, that's not bad
Dialogue: 1,0:02:31.65,0:02:33.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我就爱这种年轻人的音乐
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.65,0:02:33.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I love this young people's music
Dialogue: 1,0:02:36.51,0:02:37.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我投降
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.51,0:02:37.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I surrender
Dialogue: 1,0:02:38.80,0:02:39.71,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.80,0:02:39.71,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:02:42.85,0:02:45.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥  你怎么往你鼻子上戴我帽子
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.85,0:02:45.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Squidward, why are you wearing my hat on your nose?
Dialogue: 1,0:02:45.17,0:02:47.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我才没往我鼻子戴你帽子
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.17,0:02:47.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm not wearing your hat on my nose
Dialogue: 1,0:02:47.07,0:02:49.89,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我是在等17号的餐
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.07,0:02:49.89,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm waiting for number 17's order
Dialogue: 1,0:02:49.89,0:02:50.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,17号
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.89,0:02:50.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Number 17
Dialogue: 1,0:02:50.92,0:02:52.68,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蟹黄堡跟中杯饮料
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.92,0:02:52.68,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Krabby Patty and a medium beverage
Dialogue: 1,0:02:52.68,0:02:53.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.68,0:02:53.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Of course
Dialogue: 1,0:02:53.77,0:02:54.64,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,抱歉  章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.77,0:02:54.64,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sorry, Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:02:54.64,0:02:56.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我今天感觉不太好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.64,0:02:56.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm not really feeling myself today
Dialogue: 1,0:02:56.22,0:02:57.48,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我应该有点大惊小怪了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.22,0:02:57.48,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I guess I'm a little bit jumpy
Dialogue: 1,0:02:57.48,0:02:59.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,老是在想机器人统治世界
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.48,0:02:59.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I keep thinking robots are taking over the world
Dialogue: 1,0:02:59.52,0:03:00.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,多半是因为
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.52,0:03:00.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Probably on account of
Dialogue: 1,0:03:00.10,0:03:02.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我昨晚看了机器人统治世界的电影
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.10,0:03:01.11,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,this movie I watched last night
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.11,0:03:02.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,where robots take over the world
Dialogue: 1,0:03:02.52,0:03:04.18,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我还问小蜗是不是机器人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.52,0:03:04.18,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I even asked Gary if he was a robot
Dialogue: 1,0:03:04.18,0:03:05.28,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是不是很逗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.18,0:03:05.28,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Pretty funny, huh?
Dialogue: 1,0:03:05.75,0:03:06.84,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,太逗了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.75,0:03:06.84,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hilarious
Dialogue: 1,0:03:06.84,0:03:08.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快给客人上菜
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.84,0:03:08.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Just deliver the food
Dialogue: 1,0:03:09.24,0:03:10.34,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,上菜了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.24,0:03:10.34,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,There you go
Dialogue: 1,0:03:10.34,0:03:11.08,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,请慢用
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.34,0:03:11.08,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Enjoy your
Dialogue: 1,0:03:11.67,0:03:13.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你应该不是机器人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.67,0:03:13.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Say, you're not a robot, are you?
Dialogue: 1,0:03:13.20,0:03:14.96,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我不是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.20,0:03:14.96,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No, I'm not
Dialogue: 1,0:03:14.96,0:03:17.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,睁大眼睛多留意
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.96,0:03:17.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, keep your eyes peeled
Dialogue: 1,0:03:17.05,0:03:19.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,机器人无处不在
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.05,0:03:19.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,They're everywhere
Dialogue: 1,0:03:19.42,0:03:20.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,继续工作了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.42,0:03:20.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Back to work
Dialogue: 1,0:03:22.92,0:03:25.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,感觉充满了电
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.92,0:03:25.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I feel completely recharged
Dialogue: 1,0:03:25.82,0:03:27.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好像是蟹老板的声音
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.82,0:03:27.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That sounds like Mr. Krabs
Dialogue: 1,0:03:28.92,0:03:29.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快啊  小兄弟
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.92,0:03:29.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Come on, little buddy
Dialogue: 1,0:03:29.95,0:03:32.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,能不能再放一次
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.95,0:03:32.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,play it again, please?
Dialogue: 1,0:03:32.40,0:03:33.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,再放一次吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.40,0:03:33.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,One more time
Dialogue: 1,0:03:33.52,0:03:34.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,给我放
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.52,0:03:34.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,for me
Dialogue: 1,0:03:35.33,0:03:36.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.33,0:03:36.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That was strange
Dialogue: 1,0:03:36.85,0:03:39.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蟹老板在跟他收音机说话
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.85,0:03:39.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Mr. Krabs was talking to his radio
Dialogue: 1,0:03:39.17,0:03:41.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,而且还说自己充满了电
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.17,0:03:41.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and he said he feels "recharged"
Dialogue: 1,0:03:42.35,0:03:44.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不知道的还以为他是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.35,0:03:44.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,If I didn't know better, I'd say he was
Dialogue: 1,0:03:44.30,0:03:46.06,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,机器人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.30,0:03:46.06,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,a robot
Dialogue: 1,0:03:46.63,0:03:47.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,才不会
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.63,0:03:47.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Nah
Dialogue: 1,0:03:47.67,0:03:48.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,喂  你好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.67,0:03:48.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yes, hello
Dialogue: 1,0:03:48.90,0:03:52.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不知道你能不能再放一遍那首歌
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.90,0:03:52.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I was wondering if you could play that song again
Dialogue: 1,0:03:52.66,0:03:53.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,哪一首
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.66,0:03:53.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Which one, man?
Dialogue: 1,0:03:53.77,0:03:55.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就是那首
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.77,0:03:55.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The one that goes
Dialogue: 1,0:03:55.00,0:03:56.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,哔啵啵吧  啵啵哔
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.00,0:03:56.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,"Bee-boo-boo-bop, boo-boo-beep"
Dialogue: 1,0:03:57.21,0:03:58.31,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不对  那首是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.21,0:03:58.31,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No, man, you're thinking of
Dialogue: 1,0:03:58.31,0:04:00.21,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,哔啵啵吧  啵啵吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.31,0:04:00.21,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,"Bee-boo-boo-bop, boo-boo-bop"
Dialogue: 1,0:04:00.67,0:04:02.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,哔哔啵  啵啵吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.67,0:04:02.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Bee-bee-boo, boo-boo-bop?
Dialogue: 1,0:04:02.84,0:04:03.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,哔啵啵吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.84,0:04:03.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Bee-boo-boo-bop?
Dialogue: 1,0:04:04.95,0:04:06.24,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,啵啵哔吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.95,0:04:06.24,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Boo-boo-bee-bop?
Dialogue: 1,0:04:06.83,0:04:08.19,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不是  哔啵啵哔
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.83,0:04:08.19,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Not "Bee-boo-boo-beep"?
Dialogue: 1,0:04:09.07,0:04:09.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.07,0:04:09.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Bop?
Dialogue: 1,0:04:10.44,0:04:10.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,哔
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.44,0:04:10.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Beep?
Dialogue: 1,0:04:12.03,0:04:13.19,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,啵啵吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.03,0:04:13.19,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Boo-boo-bop?
Dialogue: 1,0:04:15.70,0:04:17.19,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我的天啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.70,0:04:17.19,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, my gosh
Dialogue: 1,0:04:17.19,0:04:19.94,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蟹老板怎么哔来哔去的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.19,0:04:19.94,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Why was Mr. Krabs making all those beeping sounds?
Dialogue: 1,0:04:19.94,0:04:22.64,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,难道他是机器人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.94,0:04:22.64,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Could it be that he's a robot?
Dialogue: 1,0:04:23.42,0:04:24.61,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,才不会
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.42,0:04:24.61,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Nah
Dialogue: 1,0:04:33.60,0:04:35.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥  太可怕了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.60,0:04:35.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, Squidward, it's terrible
Dialogue: 1,0:04:36.36,0:04:37.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蟹老板
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.36,0:04:37.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Mr. Krabs
Dialogue: 1,0:04:37.63,0:04:38.83,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,跟收音机说话
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.63,0:04:38.83,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,talking to radio
Dialogue: 1,0:04:39.40,0:04:40.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,哔来哔去
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.40,0:04:40.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,beeping sounds
Dialogue: 1,0:04:40.62,0:04:41.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,跳怪舞
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.62,0:04:41.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,strange dancing
Dialogue: 1,0:04:42.47,0:04:43.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,机器人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.47,0:04:43.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,robot
Dialogue: 1,0:04:43.42,0:04:45.33,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,真棒啊  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.42,0:04:45.33,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's great, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:04:45.33,0:04:48.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不然这问题你就到厨房去解决吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.33,0:04:48.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Why don't you work on this problem back in the kitchen
Dialogue: 1,0:04:50.17,0:04:51.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我说真的  章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.17,0:04:51.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm serious, Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:04:51.82,0:04:53.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蟹老板是机器人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.82,0:04:53.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Mr. Krabs is a robot
Dialogue: 1,0:04:53.55,0:04:54.73,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,而且我能证明
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.55,0:04:54.73,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And I can prove it, too
Dialogue: 1,0:04:54.73,0:04:55.11,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你怎么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.73,0:04:55.11,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,How did you?
Dialogue: 1,0:04:55.11,0:04:55.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我想想
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.11,0:04:55.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Let's see
Dialogue: 1,0:04:55.72,0:04:56.38,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,电影里面说
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.72,0:04:56.38,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,in the movie
Dialogue: 1,0:04:56.38,0:04:58.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,机器人没有幽默感
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.38,0:04:58.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,the robots didn't have a sense of humor
Dialogue: 1,0:04:58.35,0:04:59.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不会笑
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.35,0:04:59.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,they couldn't laugh
Dialogue: 1,0:04:59.75,0:05:01.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蟹老板
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.75,0:05:01.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hey, Mr. Krabs
Dialogue: 1,0:05:01.00,0:05:02.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,怎么了  小子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.00,0:05:02.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What is it, boy?
Dialogue: 1,0:05:02.47,0:05:04.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥刚跟我讲个了特别逗的笑话
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.47,0:05:04.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Squidward just told me a hilarious joke
Dialogue: 1,0:05:04.60,0:05:06.11,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你应该会比较想听
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.60,0:05:06.11,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and I thought you might like to hear it
Dialogue: 1,0:05:06.11,0:05:07.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是这样吗  章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.11,0:05:07.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Is it true, Squidward?
Dialogue: 1,0:05:07.55,0:05:08.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,真有这么逗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.55,0:05:08.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Is it hilarious?
Dialogue: 1,0:05:09.50,0:05:11.04,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那是当然了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.50,0:05:11.04,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah, sure
Dialogue: 1,0:05:11.05,0:05:12.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那就讲吧  小子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.05,0:05:12.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, let's hear it, lad
Dialogue: 1,0:05:12.62,0:05:14.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好  开讲了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.62,0:05:14.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Okay, here it goes
Dialogue: 1,0:05:14.44,0:05:15.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,怎么讲来着  章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.44,0:05:15.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,How'd it go, Squidward?
Dialogue: 1,0:05:16.92,0:05:17.46,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.92,0:05:17.46,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It went
Dialogue: 1,0:05:18.78,0:05:19.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我想想
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.78,0:05:19.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Let's see, uh
Dialogue: 1,0:05:19.70,0:05:22.96,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,为什么11岁小朋友不能看海盗电影
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.70,0:05:22.96,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Why couldn't the 11-year-old get into the pirate movie?
Dialogue: 1,0:05:22.96,0:05:23.76,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.96,0:05:23.76,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 1,0:05:23.76,0:05:26.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,因为那是啊级片
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.76,0:05:26.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It was rated "Arr"
Dialogue: 1,0:05:30.52,0:05:31.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.52,0:05:31.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Arr
Dialogue: 1,0:05:33.47,0:05:36.04,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海盗就喜欢说  啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.47,0:05:36.04,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Because it's about pirates
Dialogue: 1,0:05:37.15,0:05:39.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我没让你上班演脱口秀  章鱼哥先生
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.15,0:05:39.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm not paying you to do stand-up, Mr. Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:05:39.92,0:05:41.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快回去工作
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.92,0:05:41.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now, get back to work
Dialogue: 1,0:05:41.92,0:05:43.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,连笑都没笑
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.92,0:05:43.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Not even a chuckle
Dialogue: 1,0:05:43.40,0:05:44.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,看吧  章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.40,0:05:44.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,See, Squidward?
Dialogue: 1,0:05:44.32,0:05:46.63,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他笑不出来  因为他不会笑
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.32,0:05:46.63,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,He didn't laugh because he couldn't laugh
Dialogue: 1,0:05:46.63,0:05:49.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他就是个机器人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.63,0:05:49.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,because he's a robot
Dialogue: 1,0:05:49.58,0:05:52.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他不笑是有道理的  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.58,0:05:51.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,There's a logical explanation
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.12,0:05:52.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,why he didn't laugh, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:05:52.57,0:05:55.08,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,很明显他以前听过了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.57,0:05:55.08,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,He's obviously heard it before
Dialogue: 1,0:05:55.08,0:05:56.99,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你之所以会觉得蟹老板是机器人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.08,0:05:56.99,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The only reason you think Krabs is a robot
Dialogue: 1,0:05:56.99,0:05:59.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,单纯是因为你看了那部破电影
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.99,0:05:59.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,is because you watched that stupid movie
Dialogue: 1,0:05:59.05,0:06:00.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,赶紧给我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.05,0:06:00.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now, why don't you
Dialogue: 1,0:06:00.05,0:06:01.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蟹老板
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.05,0:06:01.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hey, Mr. Krabs
Dialogue: 1,0:06:01.45,0:06:02.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.45,0:06:02.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 1,0:06:02.20,0:06:03.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,什么事  小子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.20,0:06:03.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What is it, boy?
Dialogue: 1,0:06:03.52,0:06:06.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥他爸从来没抱过他
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.52,0:06:06.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Squidward's father never hugged him
Dialogue: 1,0:06:07.22,0:06:08.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是不是很惨
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.22,0:06:08.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Isn't that sad?
Dialogue: 1,0:06:10.10,0:06:12.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,确实很惨
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.10,0:06:12.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yes, I suppose that is rather sad
Dialogue: 1,0:06:12.25,0:06:14.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不过章鱼哥可以休息期间自己抱自己
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.25,0:06:14.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But Squidward can hug himself during his break
Dialogue: 1,0:06:14.77,0:06:16.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快回去工作
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.77,0:06:16.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now, get back to work
Dialogue: 1,0:06:16.37,0:06:17.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,跟电影里的机器人一个样
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.37,0:06:17.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Just like the robot in the movie
Dialogue: 1,0:06:17.82,0:06:18.81,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他也不会哭
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.82,0:06:18.81,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,he couldn't cry either
Dialogue: 1,0:06:19.00,0:06:20.63,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝  越来越扯淡了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.00,0:06:20.63,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob, this is getting ridiculous
Dialogue: 1,0:06:20.63,0:06:23.19,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我跟你说  我爸非常爱我
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.63,0:06:23.19,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'll have you know my father loved me very much
Dialogue: 1,0:06:23.19,0:06:25.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那是最后一项测试  章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.19,0:06:25.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's the final test, Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:06:25.25,0:06:26.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,爱的测试
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.25,0:06:26.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,the love test
Dialogue: 1,0:06:26.52,0:06:28.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,机器人不会爱
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.52,0:06:28.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Robots can't love
Dialogue: 1,0:06:28.61,0:06:29.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,先等一下  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.61,0:06:29.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now, wait, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:06:29.60,0:06:30.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蟹老板
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.60,0:06:30.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hey, Mr. Krabs
Dialogue: 1,0:06:30.77,0:06:32.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,什么事  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.77,0:06:32.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What is it, SpongeBob?
Dialogue: 1,0:06:32.97,0:06:35.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我只想跟你说  章鱼哥爱你
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.97,0:06:35.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I just wanted to tell you that Squidward loves you
Dialogue: 1,0:06:36.50,0:06:38.41,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,回去工作  章鱼哥先生
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.50,0:06:38.41,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Get back to work, Mr. Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:06:39.95,0:06:40.83,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.95,0:06:40.83,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Squidward?
Dialogue: 1,0:06:47.17,0:06:48.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,收音机坏了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.17,0:06:48.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Me radio died
Dialogue: 1,0:06:50.00,0:06:52.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,电池还有一点点的电
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.00,0:06:52.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,These batteries still have a little juice in them
Dialogue: 1,0:06:52.17,0:06:52.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,有了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.17,0:06:52.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I know
Dialogue: 1,0:06:52.97,0:06:54.76,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,送给珍珍当圣诞礼物
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.97,0:06:54.76,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'll give them to Pearl for Christmas
Dialogue: 1,0:06:57.53,0:06:59.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,水煮蛋好了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.53,0:06:59.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Me hard-boiled egg is ready
Dialogue: 1,0:06:59.35,0:07:01.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,都快能尝得到了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.35,0:07:01.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I can already taste it
Dialogue: 1,0:07:01.81,0:07:03.44,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快到爸爸这边
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.81,0:07:03.44,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Come to Papa
Dialogue: 1,0:07:03.44,0:07:04.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,夹到了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.44,0:07:04.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Gotcha
Dialogue: 1,0:07:04.87,0:07:08.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,水煮蛋加盐才好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.87,0:07:08.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And what good is a hard-boiled egg without a little salt?
Dialogue: 1,0:07:08.47,0:07:10.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蟹老板
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.47,0:07:10.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Mr. Krabs
Dialogue: 1,0:07:12.48,0:07:13.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我的眼睛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.48,0:07:13.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,My eyes
Dialogue: 1,0:07:14.24,0:07:14.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蟹
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.24,0:07:14.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Mister
Dialogue: 1,0:07:14.75,0:07:15.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,能不能别吵了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.75,0:07:15.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Will you be quiet?
Dialogue: 1,0:07:15.87,0:07:18.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,跟我说  电影里的机器人什么样的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.87,0:07:18.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now listen, what did these robots in the movie look like?
Dialogue: 1,0:07:18.70,0:07:21.54,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,装着锐利的红眼睛  长着金属夹子手
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.70,0:07:20.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, they had piercing red eyes
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.37,0:07:21.54,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,metal pincers for hands
Dialogue: 1,0:07:21.54,0:07:22.71,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,而且用电池当能源
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.54,0:07:22.71,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and they ran on batteries
Dialogue: 1,0:07:22.71,0:07:24.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那你说说看
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.71,0:07:24.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Okay, so tell me
Dialogue: 1,0:07:24.25,0:07:27.51,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蟹老板是那个样子的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.25,0:07:27.51,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,does Mr. Krabs look anything like that?
Dialogue: 1,0:07:41.58,0:07:43.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我疏散顾客  你打给海军
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.58,0:07:43.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'll evacuate the customers, you call the Navy
Dialogue: 1,0:07:44.07,0:07:45.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,喂  接线员
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.07,0:07:45.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hello, operator
Dialogue: 1,0:07:45.27,0:07:46.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我要找海军
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.27,0:07:46.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,get me the Navy
Dialogue: 1,0:07:46.42,0:07:47.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,您好  您拨打的是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.42,0:07:47.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hello, you've reached
Dialogue: 1,0:07:47.97,0:07:50.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海军自动通话服务
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.97,0:07:50.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,the Navy's automated phone service
Dialogue: 1,0:07:50.70,0:07:53.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥  海军被机器人控制了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.70,0:07:53.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Squidward, the robots are running the Navy
Dialogue: 1,0:07:53.15,0:07:55.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海军怎么会这样
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.15,0:07:55.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Not the Navy
Dialogue: 1,0:07:55.55,0:07:57.53,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,大家注意  快逃命啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.55,0:07:57.53,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Attention, everyone, run for your lives
Dialogue: 1,0:07:57.53,0:07:59.54,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,机器人统治世界了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.53,0:07:59.54,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Robots have taken over the world
Dialogue: 1,0:08:00.96,0:08:02.46,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.96,0:08:02.46,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Our world
Dialogue: 1,0:08:07.34,0:08:08.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,现在怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.34,0:08:08.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What do we do now?
Dialogue: 1,0:08:08.52,0:08:09.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.52,0:08:09.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I don't know
Dialogue: 1,0:08:10.02,0:08:10.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,半毛钱
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.02,0:08:10.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,A nickel
Dialogue: 1,0:08:10.70,0:08:11.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.70,0:08:11.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:08:11.47,0:08:12.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.47,0:08:12.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sorry
Dialogue: 1,0:08:13.45,0:08:14.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好多了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.45,0:08:14.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's better
Dialogue: 1,0:08:15.09,0:08:17.89,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,哔啵啵哔吧  啵啵吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.09,0:08:17.89,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Bee, boo-boo-bee-boop, boo-boo-bop
Dialogue: 1,0:08:17.89,0:08:19.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一定要查出
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.89,0:08:19.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We need to find out
Dialogue: 1,0:08:19.07,0:08:21.48,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,机器人对正牌蟹老板怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.07,0:08:21.48,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,what that robot did with the real Mr. Krabs
Dialogue: 1,0:08:21.48,0:08:22.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可要怎么查
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.48,0:08:22.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,but how?
Dialogue: 1,0:08:22.27,0:08:25.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,电影主角跟好兄弟组队
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.27,0:08:25.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, in the movie the hero teams up with a buddy
Dialogue: 1,0:08:25.42,0:08:27.11,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,探查到了机器人的情报
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.42,0:08:27.11,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and they get the poop on the robot
Dialogue: 1,0:08:27.39,0:08:29.78,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他们这是擒抱机器人了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.39,0:08:29.78,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,They poop on the robot?
Dialogue: 1,0:08:29.78,0:08:31.74,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他们那是打探确切的情报
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.78,0:08:31.74,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah, you know, they get the straight poop
Dialogue: 1,0:08:31.74,0:08:33.49,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,也就是问问题  借此得到信息
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.74,0:08:33.49,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,ask questions, get information
Dialogue: 1,0:08:33.72,0:08:35.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没想到我会这么说
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.72,0:08:35.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I never thought I'd say this
Dialogue: 1,0:08:35.45,0:08:39.11,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝  我们打探情报吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.45,0:08:39.11,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,but, SpongeBob, let's get that poop
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.66,0:08:41.95,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(400,740)}用刑指南
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.29,0:08:45.25,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1072,284)}喜剧唱片
Dialogue: 1,0:08:48.07,0:08:48.96,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.07,0:08:48.96,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hello, boys
Dialogue: 1,0:08:50.08,0:08:51.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,找我干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.08,0:08:51.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What can I do for you?
Dialogue: 1,0:08:52.57,0:08:53.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你干嘛锁门
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.57,0:08:53.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Why did you lock the door?
Dialogue: 1,0:08:54.95,0:08:56.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你干嘛拿着绳子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.95,0:08:56.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Why do you have that rope?
Dialogue: 1,0:08:57.35,0:08:59.68,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谁在管收银机
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.35,0:08:59.68,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Who's watching the cash register?
Dialogue: 1,0:09:02.97,0:09:03.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.97,0:09:03.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:09:03.72,0:09:04.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.72,0:09:04.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:09:04.72,0:09:06.09,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这是什么意思
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.72,0:09:06.09,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What's the meaning of this?
Dialogue: 1,0:09:06.09,0:09:07.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,立刻给我松绑
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.09,0:09:07.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Untie me this instant
Dialogue: 1,0:09:07.70,0:09:08.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,闭嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.70,0:09:08.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Shut up
Dialogue: 1,0:09:09.32,0:09:10.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我的戴维琼斯啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.32,0:09:10.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sweet Davy Jones
Dialogue: 1,0:09:10.97,0:09:13.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这到底是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.97,0:09:13.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What the heck is going on?
Dialogue: 1,0:09:13.00,0:09:16.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,给我闭嘴  破铜烂铁
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.00,0:09:16.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I said shut up, you bucket of bolts
Dialogue: 1,0:09:16.05,0:09:17.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我受不了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.05,0:09:17.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I can't take it
Dialogue: 1,0:09:19.52,0:09:21.36,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝  你没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.52,0:09:21.36,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob, are you okay?
Dialogue: 1,0:09:21.36,0:09:24.64,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥  你那样扇蟹老板的脸
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.36,0:09:24.64,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, Squidward, seeing you slap Mr. Krabs like that
Dialogue: 1,0:09:24.64,0:09:26.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我根本不敢看
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.64,0:09:26.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,is just too horrible to watch
Dialogue: 1,0:09:26.50,0:09:29.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那根本不是蟹老板
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.50,0:09:29.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No, that's not Mr. Krabs
Dialogue: 1,0:09:29.52,0:09:31.21,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是机器螃蟹
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.52,0:09:31.21,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's Robot Krabs
Dialogue: 1,0:09:31.21,0:09:32.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,啊对
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.21,0:09:32.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah
Dialogue: 1,0:09:32.15,0:09:34.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对付这些机器人的办法
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.15,0:09:34.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And the only way to deal with these robot types
Dialogue: 1,0:09:34.25,0:09:36.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就是查出机器人所知的情报
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.25,0:09:36.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,is to find out what they know
Dialogue: 1,0:09:36.97,0:09:38.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.97,0:09:38.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Right
Dialogue: 1,0:09:40.32,0:09:43.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝  你先问他问题
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.32,0:09:43.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob, you got to ask him a question first
Dialogue: 1,0:09:43.02,0:09:44.18,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.02,0:09:44.18,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah
Dialogue: 1,0:09:44.18,0:09:45.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我内裤什么颜色的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.18,0:09:45.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What color is my underwear?
Dialogue: 1,0:09:46.30,0:09:47.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.30,0:09:47.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:09:47.05,0:09:48.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我来问
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.05,0:09:48.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,let me handle this
Dialogue: 1,0:09:48.52,0:09:50.26,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蟹老板在哪
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.52,0:09:50.26,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Where's Mr. Krabs?
Dialogue: 1,0:09:50.57,0:09:52.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你胡说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.57,0:09:52.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 1,0:09:52.15,0:09:53.58,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我就是蟹老板
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.15,0:09:53.58,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm Mr. Krabs
Dialogue: 1,0:09:54.07,0:09:56.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不从实招来就整晚扇你脸
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.07,0:09:56.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We can do this all night if you want
Dialogue: 1,0:09:56.07,0:09:57.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蟹老板在哪
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.07,0:09:57.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Where's Mr. Krabs?
Dialogue: 1,0:09:57.72,0:09:59.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我就是蟹老板
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.72,0:09:59.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm Mr. Krabs
Dialogue: 1,0:09:59.30,0:10:00.68,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蟹老板在哪
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.30,0:10:00.68,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Where's Mr. Krabs?
Dialogue: 1,0:10:00.68,0:10:02.39,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我就是蟹老板
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.68,0:10:02.39,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm Mr. Krabs
Dialogue: 1,0:10:02.39,0:10:03.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蟹老板在哪
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.39,0:10:03.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Where's Mr. Krabs?
Dialogue: 1,0:10:03.87,0:10:06.41,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我就是蟹老板
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.87,0:10:06.41,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I am Mr. Krabs
Dialogue: 1,0:10:06.57,0:10:09.38,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我就是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.57,0:10:09.38,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I am
Dialogue: 1,0:10:09.68,0:10:11.38,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这机器人还挺顽固
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.68,0:10:11.38,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This is one stubborn robot
Dialogue: 1,0:10:12.26,0:10:13.44,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.26,0:10:13.44,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 1,0:10:13.63,0:10:16.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们以为我是机器人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.63,0:10:16.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You think I'm a robot?
Dialogue: 1,0:10:16.30,0:10:17.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不是以为
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.30,0:10:17.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We don't think
Dialogue: 1,0:10:17.70,0:10:19.18,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是明知
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.70,0:10:19.18,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,we know
Dialogue: 1,0:10:19.18,0:10:21.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那可是我听过最傻的话
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.18,0:10:21.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's the silliest thing I've ever heard
Dialogue: 1,0:10:21.47,0:10:24.06,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我就是蟹老板
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.47,0:10:24.06,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I am Mr. Krabs
Dialogue: 1,0:10:24.34,0:10:25.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他就是不招
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.34,0:10:25.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,He's not cracking
Dialogue: 1,0:10:25.77,0:10:27.51,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这样绝对查不出什么情报
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.77,0:10:27.51,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We'll never get it out of him this way
Dialogue: 1,0:10:27.51,0:10:28.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我有个办法
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.51,0:10:28.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I got an idea
Dialogue: 1,0:10:28.88,0:10:30.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好好提防他  章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.88,0:10:30.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Keep an eye on him, Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:10:30.05,0:10:32.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,别中了他这位机器人的诡计
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.05,0:10:32.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Don't fall for any of his robo-tricks
Dialogue: 1,0:10:36.49,0:10:39.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,要是机器螃蟹不说蟹老板在哪
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.49,0:10:39.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,If Robot Krabs won't tell us where Mr. Krabs is
Dialogue: 1,0:10:39.52,0:10:42.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那也许他的机器小朋友会说
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.52,0:10:42.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,maybe one of his little robot friends will
Dialogue: 1,0:10:42.62,0:10:43.99,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.62,0:10:43.99,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob, uh
Dialogue: 1,0:10:43.99,0:10:44.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那是搅拌机
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.99,0:10:44.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,that's a blender
Dialogue: 1,0:10:44.97,0:10:45.39,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是没错
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.97,0:10:45.39,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah
Dialogue: 1,0:10:45.39,0:10:47.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可我看到蟹老板先前跟收音机讲话
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.39,0:10:47.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,but I saw Mr. Krabs talking with his radio before
Dialogue: 1,0:10:47.95,0:10:49.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他管它叫  小兄弟
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.95,0:10:49.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,He called it his "little buddy"
Dialogue: 1,0:10:49.60,0:10:51.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是这样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.60,0:10:51.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, really?
Dialogue: 1,0:10:51.17,0:10:53.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,把它放桌上  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.17,0:10:53.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Put it on the table, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:10:53.02,0:10:55.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们是想审问我的搅拌机吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.02,0:10:55.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You're going to interrogate my blender?
Dialogue: 1,0:10:55.60,0:10:57.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,神经病吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.60,0:10:57.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You're crazy
Dialogue: 1,0:10:57.02,0:11:01.14,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们只想知道你小兄弟手上的情报
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.02,0:11:01.14,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We're just going to see what your "little buddy" knows
Dialogue: 1,0:11:01.14,0:11:02.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不行  等等
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.14,0:11:02.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No, wait
Dialogue: 1,0:11:02.40,0:11:03.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们要对我搅拌机干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.40,0:11:03.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What are you going to do to me blender?
Dialogue: 1,0:11:03.95,0:11:05.43,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那可是花了钱的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.95,0:11:05.43,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That cost me money
Dialogue: 1,0:11:05.43,0:11:07.18,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蟹老板在哪
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.43,0:11:07.18,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Where's Mr. Krabs?
Dialogue: 1,0:11:09.31,0:11:10.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不招是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.31,0:11:10.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Not talking, eh?
Dialogue: 1,0:11:12.35,0:11:13.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.35,0:11:13.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No
Dialogue: 1,0:11:13.35,0:11:17.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那个花了我二十四块九毛五
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.35,0:11:17.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That cost me $24.95
Dialogue: 1,0:11:17.93,0:11:19.44,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,它应该没情报
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.93,0:11:19.44,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I guess it didn't know anything
Dialogue: 1,0:11:19.76,0:11:20.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,去拿烤面包机
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.76,0:11:20.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Go get the toaster
Dialogue: 1,0:11:21.94,0:11:24.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,别拿我烤面包机
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.94,0:11:24.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No, not me toaster
Dialogue: 1,0:11:24.07,0:11:26.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那个花了我三十二块五
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.07,0:11:26.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That cost me $32.50
Dialogue: 1,0:11:28.67,0:11:30.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,六十二块六七
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.67,0:11:30.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,$62.67
Dialogue: 1,0:11:32.70,0:11:33.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,四
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.70,0:11:33.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Fort
Dialogue: 1,0:11:33.95,0:11:35.59,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,其实那个是白送的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.95,0:11:35.59,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, actually, that one was a gift
Dialogue: 1,0:11:36.46,0:11:39.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.46,0:11:39.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No
Dialogue: 1,0:11:39.80,0:11:42.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,只剩最后这个机器人了  章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.80,0:11:42.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This is the last robot, Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:11:42.05,0:11:43.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.05,0:11:43.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No
Dialogue: 1,0:11:43.10,0:11:44.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,别砸我收银机
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.10,0:11:44.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Not my cash register
Dialogue: 1,0:11:44.87,0:11:46.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那可是我亲手养大的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.87,0:11:46.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I raised it myself
Dialogue: 1,0:11:46.50,0:11:49.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我买的那时候  它还只是个小计算器
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.50,0:11:49.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I got it when it was just a little calculator
Dialogue: 1,0:11:49.32,0:11:51.24,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.32,0:11:51.24,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No
Dialogue: 1,0:11:56.72,0:11:58.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你不是说机器人不会哭吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.72,0:11:58.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I thought you said robots can't cry
Dialogue: 1,0:11:58.65,0:12:00.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我还说机器人不会爱
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.65,0:12:00.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I also said they couldn't love
Dialogue: 1,0:12:00.90,0:12:04.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我把它当亲生儿子爱
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.90,0:12:04.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I loved it like it was me own
Dialogue: 1,0:12:05.38,0:12:07.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,至少他没笑
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.38,0:12:07.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,At least he's not laughing
Dialogue: 1,0:12:08.45,0:12:12.58,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我还记得我们从前一同欢笑过
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.45,0:12:12.58,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I remember the laughs we used to share
Dialogue: 1,0:12:13.48,0:12:16.71,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝  你那部电影怎么结局的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.48,0:12:16.71,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob, how did that movie of yours end?
Dialogue: 1,0:12:16.71,0:12:17.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,电影
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.71,0:12:17.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The movie?
Dialogue: 1,0:12:17.50,0:12:19.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对了  结局很精彩
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.50,0:12:19.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah, the ending was great
Dialogue: 1,0:12:19.82,0:12:22.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,结果根本就没有机器人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.82,0:12:22.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Turns out there weren't any robots after all
Dialogue: 1,0:12:22.32,0:12:23.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就只是他们的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.32,0:12:23.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It was just their
Dialogue: 1,0:12:23.52,0:12:25.34,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,想象
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.52,0:12:25.34,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,imagination
Dialogue: 1,0:12:27.62,0:12:28.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,得去喂小蜗了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.62,0:12:28.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's time to feed Gary
Dialogue: 1,0:12:37.37,0:12:40.19,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.37,0:12:40.19,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Squidward
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.28,0:12:43.82,起司 特殊标题,,0,0,0,,{\fad(398,391)\pos(730,540)}领养记
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.99,0:12:48.91,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1096,976.667)}翻译{\fnArial}: 1440kHz
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.99,0:12:46.32,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(237.802,458)\frz27.79}分镜总监
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.99,0:12:46.32,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz27.79\pos(451.802,812)}分镜
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.53,0:12:48.91,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz29.67\pos(417.802,368)}编剧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.20,0:12:51.29,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz28.1\pos(291.802,418)}动画总监
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.20,0:12:51.29,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz28.1\pos(485.802,720)}创意总监
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.20,0:12:51.29,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1034.667,976.667)}本字幕仅限学习交流\N严禁用于商业用途
Dialogue: 1,0:12:54.94,0:12:56.78,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,小蜗  报纸来了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.94,0:12:56.78,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Gary, the paper's here
Dialogue: 1,0:12:59.51,0:13:00.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这个给你  兄弟
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.51,0:13:00.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You can have this, buddy
Dialogue: 1,0:13:01.13,0:13:03.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我就只要  娱乐版
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.13,0:13:03.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,because all I need is the "entertainment section"
Dialogue: 1,0:13:10.29,0:13:12.43,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我是快乐小海绵
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.29,0:13:12.43,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I am a happy sponge
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.02,0:13:18.73,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(868,756)}裤头村新闻
Dialogue: 1,0:13:21.06,0:13:22.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我看到你拿报纸了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.06,0:13:22.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I see you got the paper
Dialogue: 1,0:13:24.17,0:13:24.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.17,0:13:24.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hey, Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:13:29.03,0:13:30.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我得走了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.03,0:13:30.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, I better get going
Dialogue: 1,0:13:30.32,0:13:31.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好  再见
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.32,0:13:31.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yep, see you later
Dialogue: 1,0:13:34.80,0:13:36.13,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.80,0:13:36.13,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What did you say?
Dialogue: 1,0:13:36.13,0:13:37.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我什么都没说
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.13,0:13:37.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I didn't say anything
Dialogue: 1,0:13:37.52,0:13:38.98,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我也什么都没说
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.52,0:13:38.98,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I didn't say anything either
Dialogue: 1,0:13:39.42,0:13:40.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那就再见了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.42,0:13:40.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,See you later, then
Dialogue: 1,0:13:41.84,0:13:43.36,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你别捣乱了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.84,0:13:43.36,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,All right, quit messing with me
Dialogue: 1,0:13:43.36,0:13:44.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你肯定说了话
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.36,0:13:44.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I know you said something
Dialogue: 1,0:13:45.58,0:13:48.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,给我捣乱的明明就是你
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.58,0:13:48.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But it is you that is messing with me
Dialogue: 1,0:13:50.06,0:13:51.89,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,原来给我们捣乱的是这个
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.06,0:13:51.89,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's what's messing with us
Dialogue: 1,0:13:52.45,0:13:54.64,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是一只扇贝宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.45,0:13:54.64,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's a baby scallop
Dialogue: 1,0:13:54.64,0:13:56.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我来好好照顾
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.64,0:13:56.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'll take care of this
Dialogue: 1,0:13:56.00,0:13:56.98,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不行  派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.00,0:13:56.98,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No, Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:13:56.98,0:13:58.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,它完全无依无靠
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.98,0:13:58.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's totally helpless
Dialogue: 1,0:13:58.32,0:14:00.94,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好像还不会飞
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.32,0:14:00.94,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It looks like he can't even fly yet
Dialogue: 1,0:14:00.94,0:14:02.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那又怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.94,0:14:02.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, what's the matter?
Dialogue: 1,0:14:02.45,0:14:03.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,它是傻吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.45,0:14:03.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Is he stupid?
Dialogue: 1,0:14:03.47,0:14:04.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不对  派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.47,0:14:04.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No, Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:14:04.35,0:14:05.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,它只是个宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.35,0:14:05.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,he's just a baby
Dialogue: 1,0:14:05.86,0:14:08.16,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,孤苦伶仃  举目无亲
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.86,0:14:08.16,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,He's all alone with no one to take care of him
Dialogue: 1,0:14:08.16,0:14:11.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不能把它落在这
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.16,0:14:11.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, we can't just leave him out here
Dialogue: 1,0:14:11.47,0:14:12.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你说得对
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.47,0:14:12.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You're right
Dialogue: 1,0:14:12.40,0:14:14.04,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,带它去菠萝屋吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.40,0:14:14.04,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Come on, let's take him into the pineapple
Dialogue: 1,0:14:15.17,0:14:17.96,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,来找找  得找个盒子给它睡
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.17,0:14:17.96,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Let's see, we need a box for him to sleep in
Dialogue: 1,0:14:18.98,0:14:20.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,进来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.98,0:14:20.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,There you go
Dialogue: 1,0:14:20.25,0:14:22.71,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这可是头等座
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.25,0:14:22.71,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's the best seat in the house
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.25,0:14:22.71,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\fs60\pos(882,920)}屁股
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.71,0:14:24.17,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(644,820)}小蜗
Dialogue: 1,0:14:24.73,0:14:25.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,让我看看
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.73,0:14:25.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Let me see
Dialogue: 1,0:14:26.59,0:14:27.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还挺可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.59,0:14:27.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's kind of cute
Dialogue: 1,0:14:29.45,0:14:31.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,小家伙好像饿了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.45,0:14:31.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I think somebody's hungry
Dialogue: 1,0:14:31.95,0:14:32.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.95,0:14:32.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Is it true?
Dialogue: 1,0:14:33.30,0:14:34.43,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你饿了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.30,0:14:34.43,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Are you hungry?
Dialogue: 1,0:14:35.72,0:14:36.98,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我正好有吃的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.72,0:14:36.98,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I've got just the thing
Dialogue: 1,0:14:36.98,0:14:38.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,想不想吃蟹黄堡啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.98,0:14:38.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,How would you like a Krabby Patty?
Dialogue: 1,0:14:40.02,0:14:42.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝  你疯了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.02,0:14:42.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob SquarePants, are you crazy?
Dialogue: 1,0:14:42.57,0:14:45.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,它这么小  还不能吃那个
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.57,0:14:45.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's not the right food for a little fellow like him
Dialogue: 1,0:14:45.52,0:14:46.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还真是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.52,0:14:46.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Of course not
Dialogue: 1,0:14:46.65,0:14:48.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我确实考虑得不周到
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.65,0:14:48.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I don't know what I was thinking
Dialogue: 1,0:14:48.22,0:14:50.68,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,它要吃小号的蟹黄堡
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.22,0:14:50.68,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,He needs a tiny Krabby Patty
Dialogue: 1,0:14:53.79,0:14:56.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,从来没有谁会拒绝蟹黄堡
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.79,0:14:56.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No one's ever turned down one of these down before
Dialogue: 1,0:14:57.79,0:14:59.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,尝一尝甜甜圈
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.79,0:14:59.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Let's try a doughnut
Dialogue: 1,0:15:00.50,0:15:01.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,薯条
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.50,0:15:01.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,French fries?
Dialogue: 1,0:15:03.05,0:15:04.13,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,甜甜圈
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.05,0:15:04.13,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,A doughnut?
Dialogue: 1,0:15:05.07,0:15:06.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就只剩下这颗苹果了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.07,0:15:06.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,All we have left is this apple
Dialogue: 1,0:15:07.24,0:15:09.76,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海洋生物大家好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.24,0:15:09.76,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hello, sea creatures
Dialogue: 1,0:15:09.76,0:15:13.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我为你们带来苹果世界的问候
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.76,0:15:13.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I bring you greetings from Apple World
Dialogue: 1,0:15:14.35,0:15:15.86,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那当然了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.35,0:15:15.86,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Of course
Dialogue: 1,0:15:15.86,0:15:17.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,扇贝爱吃虫子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.86,0:15:17.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Scallops love worms
Dialogue: 1,0:15:18.15,0:15:18.89,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.15,0:15:18.89,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Wait
Dialogue: 1,0:15:19.40,0:15:22.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们要埋了你
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.40,0:15:22.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We will bury you
Dialogue: 1,0:15:23.15,0:15:25.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这下你之后应该就能好好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.15,0:15:25.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, you should be good for the rest
Dialogue: 1,0:15:26.44,0:15:27.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,又怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.44,0:15:27.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What now?
Dialogue: 1,0:15:27.57,0:15:28.69,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.57,0:15:28.69,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I don't know
Dialogue: 1,0:15:30.67,0:15:31.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,别哭了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.67,0:15:31.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Don't cry
Dialogue: 1,0:15:33.37,0:15:35.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快想办法  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.37,0:15:35.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Do something, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:15:39.04,0:15:40.68,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快看鬼脸
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.04,0:15:40.68,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Look at the funny face
Dialogue: 1,0:15:41.87,0:15:43.78,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快看鬼脸
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.87,0:15:43.78,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Look at the funny face
Dialogue: 1,0:15:44.55,0:15:46.88,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快看鬼脸
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.55,0:15:46.88,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Look at the funny face
Dialogue: 1,0:15:46.88,0:15:47.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.88,0:15:47.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Wait
Dialogue: 1,0:15:47.67,0:15:49.51,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我应该知道问题出在哪了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.67,0:15:49.51,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I think I might know the problem
Dialogue: 1,0:15:51.17,0:15:53.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这样就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.17,0:15:53.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yep, that's it all right
Dialogue: 1,0:15:53.27,0:15:55.34,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,先等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.27,0:15:55.34,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hold on just one second
Dialogue: 1,0:15:56.12,0:15:57.89,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好了  焕然一新
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.12,0:15:57.89,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Here he is, good as new
Dialogue: 1,0:15:59.56,0:16:01.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你怎么知道要这样
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.56,0:16:01.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,How did you know?
Dialogue: 1,0:16:01.00,0:16:02.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不然你以为呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.00,0:16:02.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,How do you think?
Dialogue: 1,0:16:04.27,0:16:08.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我已经快一年都自己包尿布了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.27,0:16:08.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And I been doing it all by myself for almost a year
Dialogue: 1,0:16:09.32,0:16:10.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,真高兴你能在这
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.32,0:16:10.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm sure glad you're here
Dialogue: 1,0:16:10.82,0:16:13.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我知道  幸好有我们两个
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.82,0:16:13.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I know, good thing there's two of us
Dialogue: 1,0:16:13.42,0:16:14.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,跟你说  派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.42,0:16:14.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You know, Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:16:14.72,0:16:16.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,既然这只扇贝没有父母
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.72,0:16:16.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,since this scallop doesn't have parents
Dialogue: 1,0:16:16.90,0:16:18.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那我们就应该亲手抚养它
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.90,0:16:18.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,we should raise it ourselves
Dialogue: 1,0:16:18.35,0:16:21.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是啊  至少得养到它会独立生活才行
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.35,0:16:21.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah, at least till it's old enough to be on its own
Dialogue: 1,0:16:21.92,0:16:23.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我要当妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.92,0:16:23.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I want to be the mom
Dialogue: 1,0:16:23.12,0:16:25.14,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你应该当不了妈妈  派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.12,0:16:25.14,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I don't think you can be the mom, Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:16:25.14,0:16:26.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,毕竟你可从来不穿上衣
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.14,0:16:26.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,because you never wear a shirt
Dialogue: 1,0:16:26.67,0:16:27.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,确实
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.67,0:16:27.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You're right
Dialogue: 1,0:16:28.65,0:16:32.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我当妈还确实很不幸
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.65,0:16:32.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,If I was a mom, this would be kind of shocking
Dialogue: 1,0:16:33.85,0:16:35.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就叫我爸爸吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.85,0:16:35.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Just call me "Daddy"
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.57,0:16:57.74,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1144,822)}冰淇淋
Dialogue: 1,0:17:17.91,0:17:20.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,它睡着的样子真可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.91,0:17:20.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It sure is cute when it's asleep
Dialogue: 1,0:17:20.27,0:17:21.14,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.27,0:17:21.14,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah
Dialogue: 1,0:17:29.57,0:17:30.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.57,0:17:30.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hey, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:17:32.05,0:17:32.99,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,怎么了  派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.05,0:17:32.99,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yes, Patrick?
Dialogue: 1,0:17:32.99,0:17:36.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没想到当家长这么好玩
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.99,0:17:36.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I never thought being a parent could be this much fun
Dialogue: 1,0:17:36.55,0:17:37.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我也没想到
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.55,0:17:37.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Me neither
Dialogue: 1,0:17:37.32,0:17:39.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,晚安了  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.32,0:17:39.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, good night, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:17:39.05,0:17:40.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,晚安  派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.05,0:17:40.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Good night, Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:17:42.70,0:17:44.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星  早餐做好了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.70,0:17:44.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Patrick, breakfast is ready
Dialogue: 1,0:17:46.67,0:17:48.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好耶
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.67,0:17:48.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,All right
Dialogue: 1,0:17:48.22,0:17:50.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,当家长养孩子让我饿坏了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.22,0:17:50.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,All this parenting stuff makes me hungry
Dialogue: 1,0:17:55.16,0:17:57.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,小宝贝  今天好不好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.16,0:17:57.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hey, Junior, how you doing today?
Dialogue: 1,0:17:59.40,0:18:00.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.40,0:18:00.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob?
Dialogue: 1,0:18:00.40,0:18:01.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,什么事  派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.40,0:18:01.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yes, Patrick?
Dialogue: 1,0:18:01.87,0:18:03.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,孩子拉臭臭了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.87,0:18:03.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Kid's got a stinky
Dialogue: 1,0:18:03.27,0:18:04.34,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你能帮忙换尿布吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.27,0:18:04.34,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Could you take care of him?
Dialogue: 1,0:18:04.34,0:18:05.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我手没空
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.34,0:18:05.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,My hands are kind of full
Dialogue: 1,0:18:08.06,0:18:09.69,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我是很想  但我得走了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.06,0:18:09.69,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Wish I could, but I got to get going
Dialogue: 1,0:18:09.69,0:18:10.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,走了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.69,0:18:10.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Going?
Dialogue: 1,0:18:10.57,0:18:11.69,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你要去哪
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.57,0:18:11.69,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Where are you going?
Dialogue: 1,0:18:11.69,0:18:12.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,去上班
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.69,0:18:12.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Going to work
Dialogue: 1,0:18:12.67,0:18:14.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我当爸爸  忘了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.67,0:18:14.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm the dad, remember?
Dialogue: 1,0:18:14.60,0:18:17.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你是说我得自个儿照看小宝宝吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.60,0:18:17.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You mean I have to do all this baby stuff myself?
Dialogue: 1,0:18:17.57,0:18:19.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,晚上回来就让你休息
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.57,0:18:19.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'll give you a break tonight when I get home
Dialogue: 1,0:18:19.82,0:18:22.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们两位要一直可爱下去哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.82,0:18:22.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Don't you two stop being adorable
Dialogue: 1,0:18:24.66,0:18:25.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.66,0:18:25.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Okay
Dialogue: 1,0:18:33.20,0:18:34.59,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好漫长的一天
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.20,0:18:34.59,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What a day
Dialogue: 1,0:18:34.59,0:18:36.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,太棒了  你回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.59,0:18:36.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, great, you're home
Dialogue: 1,0:18:36.57,0:18:38.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可以帮我照看小宝贝了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.57,0:18:38.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now you can help me with the baby
Dialogue: 1,0:18:38.42,0:18:40.74,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝  我是很想
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.42,0:18:40.74,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Gee, SpongeBob, I'd love to
Dialogue: 1,0:18:40.74,0:18:42.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可我上班太累了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.74,0:18:42.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,but I'm totally beat from work
Dialogue: 1,0:18:49.77,0:18:52.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那家伙脑袋给椰子砸着了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.77,0:18:52.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That guy got hit in the head with a coconut
Dialogue: 1,0:18:52.35,0:18:54.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星  那我还休息吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.35,0:18:54.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Patrick, what about my break?
Dialogue: 1,0:18:54.50,0:18:56.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,啊对  你要休息
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.50,0:18:56.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah, your break
Dialogue: 1,0:18:56.07,0:18:57.69,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,保证明天肯定会
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.07,0:18:57.69,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Tomorrow, I promise
Dialogue: 1,0:18:58.93,0:19:00.53,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好吧  明天
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.93,0:19:00.53,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Okay, tomorrow
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.53,0:19:01.99,标准-Chi,,0,0,75,,明天
Dialogue: 1,0:19:03.72,0:19:05.83,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,劳累的一天又结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.72,0:19:05.83,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Another tough day
Dialogue: 1,0:19:06.66,0:19:10.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星  真高兴你上班一整天回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.66,0:19:10.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Patrick, I'm so glad you're home after working all day
Dialogue: 1,0:19:10.67,0:19:12.41,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我等不及要休息了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.67,0:19:12.41,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I can't wait for my break
Dialogue: 1,0:19:12.41,0:19:14.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,上班累死我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.41,0:19:14.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Work was a killer
Dialogue: 1,0:19:14.37,0:19:15.63,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我得找椅子坐
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.37,0:19:15.63,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I need my chair
Dialogue: 1,0:19:16.42,0:19:18.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星  我真的需要
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.42,0:19:18.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Patrick, I really need my
Dialogue: 1,0:19:18.47,0:19:20.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,明天一定
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.47,0:19:20.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Tomorrow for sure
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.63,0:19:22.64,标准-Chi,,0,0,75,,明天一定
Dialogue: 1,0:19:23.70,0:19:24.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.70,0:19:24.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Patrick?
Dialogue: 1,0:19:25.60,0:19:27.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我终归会去做的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.60,0:19:27.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'll get to it eventually
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.97,0:19:30.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,75,,终归
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.69,0:19:36.86,标准-Chi,,0,0,75,,呃
Dialogue: 1,0:19:37.99,0:19:39.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星  我们得谈谈
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.99,0:19:39.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Patrick Star, we need to talk
Dialogue: 1,0:19:39.70,0:19:40.66,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,再等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.70,0:19:40.66,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Just one more minute
Dialogue: 1,0:19:40.66,0:19:41.09,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我得
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.66,0:19:41.09,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I got to
Dialogue: 1,0:19:41.09,0:19:43.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,别搁那等一下了  大老爷
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.09,0:19:43.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Don't "one more minute" me, Mr. Man
Dialogue: 1,0:19:43.51,0:19:45.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你害我要错过椰子了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.51,0:19:45.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm missing the coconut
Dialogue: 1,0:19:45.02,0:19:47.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你根本就没帮忙养小宝贝
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.02,0:19:47.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You haven't been helping at all with Junior
Dialogue: 1,0:19:47.12,0:19:48.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,都已经做过保证了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.12,0:19:48.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We made a commitment
Dialogue: 1,0:19:48.20,0:19:49.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,结果你该干的活还是没干
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.20,0:19:49.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and you're not doing your share
Dialogue: 1,0:19:49.82,0:19:51.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你什么都没做
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.82,0:19:51.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You never do anything
Dialogue: 1,0:19:51.30,0:19:52.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我给它换了尿布
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.30,0:19:52.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I changed his diaper
Dialogue: 1,0:19:52.65,0:19:53.88,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,才一次
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.65,0:19:53.88,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah, once
Dialogue: 1,0:19:53.88,0:19:55.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,它才这么大
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.88,0:19:55.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,He's only this big
Dialogue: 1,0:19:55.67,0:19:58.34,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,能用多少尿布
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.67,0:19:58.34,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,How many diapers can he possibly use?
Dialogue: 1,0:20:00.17,0:20:01.34,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那又不多
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.17,0:20:01.34,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's not so much
Dialogue: 1,0:20:03.07,0:20:03.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,又怎样
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.07,0:20:03.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,So?
Dialogue: 1,0:20:15.30,0:20:17.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我都不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.30,0:20:17.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I had no idea
Dialogue: 1,0:20:17.92,0:20:21.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我算什么爸爸啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.92,0:20:21.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What kind of father am I?
Dialogue: 1,0:20:22.13,0:20:23.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我一定会补偿你的  兄弟
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.13,0:20:23.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'll make it up to you, buddy
Dialogue: 1,0:20:24.17,0:20:25.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我保证
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.17,0:20:25.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I promise
Dialogue: 1,0:20:26.56,0:20:28.99,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那你今天有什么计划
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.56,0:20:28.99,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,So, what's the plan for today?
Dialogue: 1,0:20:28.99,0:20:30.99,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,再也不鬼混了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.99,0:20:30.99,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No more fooling around
Dialogue: 1,0:20:31.24,0:20:33.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,从现在起  我就是超级老爸
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.24,0:20:33.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,From now on, I'm Superdad
Dialogue: 1,0:20:33.72,0:20:35.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我上班上到下午就走
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.72,0:20:35.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'll work straight through lunch
Dialogue: 1,0:20:35.05,0:20:36.91,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这样就能准时回家了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.05,0:20:36.91,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,so I can get home on time
Dialogue: 1,0:20:36.91,0:20:40.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一定要留个大个臭尿布给我换
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.91,0:20:37.59,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,So make sure
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.59,0:20:40.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,you save a big old stinky diaper for me to change
Dialogue: 1,0:20:40.92,0:20:43.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,让你晚上好好休息
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.92,0:20:43.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And you could take the night off, pal
Dialogue: 1,0:20:43.62,0:20:45.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,太棒了  那就六点见
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.62,0:20:45.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Great, so I'll see you at 6:00
Dialogue: 1,0:20:46.26,0:20:47.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,六点见
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.26,0:20:47.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,6:00
Dialogue: 1,0:20:47.47,0:20:48.48,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,六点见
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.47,0:20:48.48,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,6:00
Dialogue: 1,0:20:48.70,0:20:49.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,六点见
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.70,0:20:49.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,6:00
Dialogue: 1,0:20:50.21,0:20:51.39,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,六点见
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.21,0:20:51.39,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,6:00
Dialogue: 1,0:20:51.65,0:20:52.89,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,六点见
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.65,0:20:52.89,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,6:00
Dialogue: 1,0:20:53.13,0:20:54.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,六点见
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.13,0:20:54.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,6:00
Dialogue: 1,0:20:54.67,0:20:55.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,六点见
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.67,0:20:55.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,6:00
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.98,0:20:58.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,75,,半夜十二点
Dialogue: 1,0:21:03.04,0:21:04.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,玩得真爽
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.04,0:21:04.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Boy, that was some party
Dialogue: 1,0:21:04.98,0:21:06.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.98,0:21:06.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hey, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:21:06.27,0:21:07.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,小宝贝
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.27,0:21:07.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hey, Junior
Dialogue: 1,0:21:09.02,0:21:09.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,咋了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.02,0:21:09.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 1,0:21:10.46,0:21:11.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,咋了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.46,0:21:11.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 1,0:21:11.74,0:21:12.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没事
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.74,0:21:12.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Nothing
Dialogue: 1,0:21:12.79,0:21:13.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那就放心了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.79,0:21:13.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What a relief
Dialogue: 1,0:21:13.55,0:21:16.06,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我刚还以为你对我发火了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.55,0:21:16.06,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,For a second, I thought you were mad at me
Dialogue: 1,0:21:16.31,0:21:18.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你还记得早上对我说了什么吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.31,0:21:18.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Do you remember what you said to me this morning?
Dialogue: 1,0:21:18.25,0:21:20.13,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,说的是根啤吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.25,0:21:20.13,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Something about root beer, right?
Dialogue: 1,0:21:21.49,0:21:22.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不对
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.49,0:21:22.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No
Dialogue: 1,0:21:22.69,0:21:23.34,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,先等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.69,0:21:23.34,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Wait, wait
Dialogue: 1,0:21:23.34,0:21:24.24,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我猜猜看
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.34,0:21:24.24,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Let me guess
Dialogue: 1,0:21:25.02,0:21:25.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不会猜
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.02,0:21:25.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I give up
Dialogue: 1,0:21:25.92,0:21:28.93,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,让你晚上好好休息
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.92,0:21:28.93,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Does "You could take the night off, pal"
Dialogue: 1,0:21:28.93,0:21:29.93,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还有没有印象
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.93,0:21:29.93,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,ring a bell?
Dialogue: 1,0:21:30.64,0:21:32.14,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我才用不着
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.64,0:21:32.14,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I don't need this
Dialogue: 1,0:21:32.76,0:21:33.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.76,0:21:33.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 1,0:21:33.97,0:21:35.56,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你这是想去哪
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.97,0:21:35.56,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Where do you think you're going?
Dialogue: 1,0:21:36.35,0:21:38.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我要回去上班
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.35,0:21:38.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm going back to work
Dialogue: 1,0:21:40.00,0:21:40.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,上班
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.00,0:21:40.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Work?
Dialogue: 1,0:21:46.10,0:21:49.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他脑袋给两个椰子砸着了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.10,0:21:49.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,He got hit in the head with two coconuts
Dialogue: 1,0:21:49.00,0:21:49.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,原来
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.00,0:21:49.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,So
Dialogue: 1,0:21:49.72,0:21:51.49,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是上这么个班
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.72,0:21:51.49,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,this is work?
Dialogue: 1,0:21:51.49,0:21:53.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,看着简单  做起来难
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.49,0:21:53.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You know, it's not as easy as it looks
Dialogue: 1,0:21:53.75,0:21:56.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,有时候得挪天线
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.75,0:21:56.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sometimes I got to move the antenna
Dialogue: 1,0:21:56.25,0:21:58.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,有时候会丢掉遥控器
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.25,0:21:58.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,sometimes I lose the remote
Dialogue: 1,0:21:58.27,0:22:01.13,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,有时候我屁股会特别痒
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.27,0:22:01.13,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and sometimes my butt itches real bad
Dialogue: 1,0:22:01.71,0:22:03.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好可怜啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.71,0:22:03.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You poor, poor thing
Dialogue: 1,0:22:03.45,0:22:05.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,顺带一提  你忘带公文包了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.45,0:22:05.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,By the way, you forgot your briefcase
Dialogue: 1,0:22:10.18,0:22:14.14,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,原来这就是我加班的回报啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.18,0:22:14.14,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,So this is the thanks I get for working overtime?
Dialogue: 1,0:22:15.27,0:22:16.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,加班
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.27,0:22:16.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Overtime?
Dialogue: 1,0:22:16.40,0:22:17.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没错  就加班了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.40,0:22:17.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah, overtime, pal
Dialogue: 1,0:22:17.30,0:22:18.39,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是啊  你还上班呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.30,0:22:18.39,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, boy, yeah, you're working
Dialogue: 1,0:22:18.39,0:22:19.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,知道什么意思吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.39,0:22:19.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You know what that means?
Dialogue: 1,0:22:19.12,0:22:20.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你就上这种班啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.12,0:22:20.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And that's the kind of work you're doing?
Dialogue: 1,0:22:20.00,0:22:20.94,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,累了摸个鱼也算上班
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.00,0:22:20.94,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It means working when you're too tired to work
Dialogue: 1,0:22:20.94,0:22:21.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那就带我签合同啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.94,0:22:21.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Show me where to sign up for it
Dialogue: 1,0:22:21.92,0:22:22.94,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我好歹都拼命在养孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.92,0:22:22.94,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,because I've been working my fingers to the bone
Dialogue: 1,0:22:22.94,0:22:23.89,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那你就继续养下去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.94,0:22:23.89,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You just keep going on working and working
Dialogue: 1,0:22:23.89,0:22:24.78,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你从来没帮过我
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.89,0:22:24.78,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You never helped
Dialogue: 1,0:22:24.78,0:22:25.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没帮过
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.78,0:22:25.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Never
Dialogue: 1,0:22:27.96,0:22:30.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,又是那个鬼噪音
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.96,0:22:30.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,There's that stupid noise again
Dialogue: 1,0:22:31.08,0:22:32.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那不是鬼噪音
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.08,0:22:32.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's not a stupid noise
Dialogue: 1,0:22:32.25,0:22:34.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是小宝贝要跳二楼窗户了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.25,0:22:33.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's just Junior
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.12,0:22:34.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,about to jump out that two-story window
Dialogue: 1,0:22:37.40,0:22:39.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,小宝贝
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.40,0:22:39.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Junior
Dialogue: 1,0:22:40.79,0:22:41.41,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,小宝贝快过来
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.79,0:22:41.41,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Here, darling
Dialogue: 1,0:22:41.41,0:22:42.06,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们来救你了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.41,0:22:42.06,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Here we come, buddy
Dialogue: 1,0:22:42.90,0:22:44.13,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,过来爸爸这儿
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.90,0:22:44.13,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Come to Daddy
Dialogue: 1,0:22:45.22,0:22:46.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我会接到你的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.22,0:22:46.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna get you
Dialogue: 1,0:22:50.53,0:22:51.73,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你接到了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.53,0:22:51.73,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Did you catch him?
Dialogue: 1,0:22:52.07,0:22:53.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没有
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.07,0:22:53.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No
Dialogue: 1,0:22:54.10,0:22:57.48,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们不是好家长
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.10,0:22:57.48,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We're bad parents
Dialogue: 1,0:23:06.42,0:23:07.61,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,小宝贝
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.42,0:23:07.61,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Junior?
Dialogue: 1,0:23:07.61,0:23:10.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,它飞起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.61,0:23:10.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,He's flying
Dialogue: 1,0:23:10.55,0:23:12.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,看来它长大了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.55,0:23:12.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I guess he's all grown up
Dialogue: 1,0:23:16.28,0:23:17.91,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那爸爸呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.28,0:23:17.91,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What about Daddy?
Dialogue: 1,0:23:20.64,0:23:22.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,真乖
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.64,0:23:22.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's my boy
Dialogue: 1,0:23:23.15,0:23:24.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,再见
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.15,0:23:24.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Good-bye
Dialogue: 1,0:23:24.62,0:23:26.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,再见  小宝贝
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.62,0:23:26.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Good-bye, Junior
Dialogue: 1,0:23:26.42,0:23:29.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星  它再也不需要我们了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.42,0:23:29.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, Patrick, he doesn't need us anymore
Dialogue: 1,0:23:29.65,0:23:33.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,天下父母最难面对别离
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.65,0:23:33.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This is the hardest part of every parent's life
Dialogue: 1,0:23:33.22,0:23:34.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我是这么看的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.22,0:23:34.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I assume
Dialogue: 1,0:23:34.72,0:23:38.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,尽管历经挫折  依然值得
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.72,0:23:38.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Despite all we've been through, it was worth it
Dialogue: 1,0:23:38.22,0:23:39.33,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.22,0:23:39.33,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah
Dialogue: 1,0:23:40.22,0:23:41.88,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,再养一只吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.22,0:23:41.88,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Let's have another
